<html><head><title>Hunt</title></head> <body bgcolor="#000000" text="#FFFFFF" vlink = "#99cccc" link = "#99ccff"  topmargin=0leftmargin=0 ><TABLE border = "0" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="5"><TR><TD valign = middle align = left  height = 300 ><font size="+1">Hue Phu Bi . There have been some pictures of a Marine Huey shot down atthat LZ in a lot of photos that I've see since the war. All four men diedin that direct mortar hit. And we carried on as <A HREF = "hunt5.html">life asusual...</A> You got that way after a while.</font> <p>JJoel Hunt Sr.</TD></TR></table></body></html>